This paper deals with cryptography and communication systems, which are typically covered by the Information Theory (cs.IT), Cryptography and Security (cs.CR), and Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) sub-categories. The paper also involves signal processing and optimization techniques, which are relevant to the Signal Processing (cs.SY) and Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
